{"authorDailyContributionsMap":{"Depsheng":[{"date":"2026-04-13T00:00:00","commitResults":[{"hash":"09f9c599fc8aa216f8baef5545f3979dd844d1ba","isMergeCommit":false,"messageTitle":"Improve meeting cleanup notifications and confirmation handling","messageBody":"Adds a startup result message when past meetings are removed from saved data, so users are informed instead of the cleanup happening silently. Also improves meeting clearing and confirmation flows by returning a clear “no meeting to clear” message when applicable, and by warning users that commands are locked while delete/clear confirmation is pending unless they enter y or n.\n","fileTypesAndContributionMap":{"functional-code":{"insertions":74,"deletions":10}}},{"hash":"a0ce592bac5909e5697d4eed6c30620abc9ce073","isMergeCommit":false,"messageTitle":"Add tests for meeting cleanup and confirmation locking","messageBody":"Adds coverage for recent meeting and confirmation beheavior, including invalid delete/clear confirmation inputs locking other commands, clearing a person with no scheduled meeting, and tracking/removing past meetings during JSON loading.\n","fileTypesAndContributionMap":{"test-code":{"insertions":69,"deletions":0}}},{"hash":"92810d5eb51e0bc6154add649424d0bda07593d9","isMergeCommit":false,"messageTitle":"Improve coverage for meeting and confirmation fixes","messageBody":"Adds targeted tests for the recent bug fixes, including startup past-meeting notification handling, save-failure behavior during cleanup, and modifiesAddressBook() coverage for delete and meeting commands.\n","fileTypesAndContributionMap":{"test-code":{"insertions":109,"deletions":0}}},{"hash":"05dae07acafb01a1b58c428048a98e48570a912c","isMergeCommit":false,"messageTitle":"Update documentation for command behavior and planned enhancements","messageBody":"Clarifies command behavior in the User Guide and Developer Guide, including case-insensitive y/n confirmations, trailing-argument handling for no-argument commands, and clear reje