ings” message when users run meeting INDEX clear on a contact without a meeting.\n•\nAdding tests for confirmation locking, clear-with-no-meeting behavior, and address book modification coverage.\n•\nAdding a DG planned enhancement that past meetings are currently removed on app open, and future iterations will notify users when that cleanup happens.\n","fileTypesAndContributionMap":{"functional-code":{"insertions":11,"deletions":4},"docs":{"insertions":2,"deletions":0},"test-code":{"insertions":63,"deletions":0}}},{"hash":"1a2c5f46a965be443dfd233497eb19a357a7ca0f","isMergeCommit":true,"messageTitle":"Merge pull request #259 from Depsheng/add-additional-notifications","messageBody":"Add confirmation-lock handling, clearer meeting cleanup behavior, and…","fileTypesAndContributionMap":{}},{"hash":"ec18dda3e4ff8240ce9884c7507523098c7bc262","isMergeCommit":false,"messageTitle":"Changed Clear and DeleteCommand","messageBody":"Updated Clear and deletecommand to better reflect the trimming of confirmation command\n","fileTypesAndContributionMap":{"functional-code":{"insertions":6,"deletions":4},"docs":{"insertions":1,"deletions":1},"test-code":{"insertions":2,"deletions":2}}},{"hash":"d70da5fe27ad53f4c2ee3f0db95bc692e2fb6d97","isMergeCommit":true,"messageTitle":"Merge pull request #260 from Depsheng/add-additional-notifications","messageBody":"Changed Clear and DeleteCommand","fileTypesAndContributionMap":{}}]}],"Just-Chocomint":[{"date":"2026-04-12T00:00:00","commitResults":[{"hash":"54e59d1f01a0e4513394a10610799fcb387e5142","isMergeCommit":false,"messageTitle":"Fix leap year parsing","messageBody":"Leap year was getting incorrectly rejected by DateTimeUtil.\n","fileTypesAndContributionMap":{"functional-code":{"insertions":10,"deletions":1}}},{"hash":"847f27c278ecd7e7755c49aa9d380c95cad9e6e9","isMergeCommit":false,"messageTitle":"Fix some date formats getting rejected","messageBody":"Some date formats were getting incorrectly rejected\n- 16 dec 2026 16:00\n- 16 dec 16:00\